<% include partials/page-top %>


  <!-- game -->
  <div class="row justify-content-center text-center mt-4" id="gameBoard">
    <div class="col">
		  <h2 class="mb-4 mx-2">Let the blood bath begin!</h2>
  		<ul class="list-unstyled">
  			<li class="mt-5"><button type="button" class="btn btn-xl btn-primary play">Play <i class="fas fa-play-circle"></i></button></li>
  			<li class="mt-4"><button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#instructionsModal">Instructions <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i></button></li>
  		</ul>
    </div>
	</div>


  <!-- instructions modal -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="instructionsModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="Instructions" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close" id="play">
            <span aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i></span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <p>You will be presented with two combatants in the form of movies from the American Film Institute's Top 100 American Movies.</p>

          <p>To beatdown your opponent and reward your hero (i.e. the movie you prefer), simply click your favorite of the two.</p>

          <p>A progress meter is displayed under your combatants. It may take awhile, but persevere and you'll end up a ranking of all your heroes and their fallen foes.</p>

          <p>To commence your Movie Beatdown, simply click the play button below.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer justify-content-center">
          <button type="button" data-dismiss="modal" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary play">Play <i class="fas fa-play-circle"></i></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


<% include partials/page-bottom %>
